rows.label: qst200220_msg0001
rows.name:
We're looking for an Superbian woman
named Harghal. She's been smuggling
Pollen Orb ingredients into Luxuria.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0002
rows.name: Do you know anything about her?

rows.label: qst200220_msg0003
rows.name:
Sure, I know her. You don't see
many Superbian women around
these parts, after all.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0004
rows.name:
I believe her cargo was taken to over
near the Old Gelgemos Gate.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0005
rows.name:
Seems like she's making something
over there.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0007
rows.name:
Perhaps, perhaps...
I'm afraid I don't have any sources
on the precise details.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0008
rows.name: I see. Well, thanks for the help.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0009
rows.name:
The Old Gelgemos Gate, huh...?
I guess it would be quickest to go
via Genbu Drifts.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0010
rows.name:
Sounds about right. At any rate,
looks like we're finally getting close
to catching this Harghal girl!

rows.label: qst200220_msg0011
rows.name:
Yeah! Not long until we get to see
her in person! Let's do this!
